## Preparation
Set-up chunk
```{r}
knitr::opts_chunk$set(message = FALSE, warning = FALSE)
```

Load libraries
```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(here)
```

Read in Data
```{r}
# read in tree ring data
rwi_long <- read_csv(here("~/../../capstone/climatree/dataverse-archive/rwi_long.csv"))

# view header
head(rwi_long, 2)
```
